snippet.title: Best VGM 2185 - Jet Set Radio - Sweet Soul Brother
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Dreamcast / PC / PS3 / X360 / Etc.
Jet Set Radio / Jet Grind Radio (2000)
Sweet Soul Brother
Hideki Naganuma
